      "value": "<p>You gain @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.feats.Item.vzpE4Q8u5TQHNVP1]{Creature Companion Master} as a bonus feat, even if you don’t meet the prerequisites. In addition, if you become @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.lf8pbezocjYIvR9y]{unconscious}, your active creature companion automatically moves in the safest manner possible until it’s adjacent to you. If it’s your size or larger, it then uses a special full action to move up to half of its speed away from combat toward safety, dragging you along with it. If your companion is smaller than you, it instead provides you with cover until the start of your next turn.</p>"
